&lt;H2&gt;Information and guidelines for reviewers&lt;/H2&gt; " ID="1-1-2-2" order="29"/></LayoutNode></LayoutNode><LayoutNode FrameSourceIndex="0" SourceIndex="56;59;62;64;66;68" DoC="9" ContainImg="0" IsImg="false" ContainTable="false" ContainP="5" TextLen="1664" LinkTextLen="0" DOMCldNum="6" FontSize="12" FontWeight="400" BgColor="transparent" ObjectRectLeft="10" ObjectRectTop="632" ObjectRectWidth="413" ObjectRectHeight="653" ID="1-2" order="30"><LayoutNode FrameSourceIndex="0" SourceIndex="56;59;62;64;66" DoC="9" ContainImg="0" IsImg="false" ContainTable="false" ContainP="5" TextLen="1648" LinkTextLen="0" DOMCldNum="5" FontSize="12" FontWeight="400" BgColor="transparent" ObjectRectLeft="10" ObjectRectTop="632" ObjectRectWidth="413" ObjectRectHeight="608" ID="1-2-1" order="31"><LayoutNode FrameSourceIndex="0" SourceIndex="56" DoC="10" ContainImg="0" IsImg="false" ContainTable="false" ContainP="0" TextLen="328" LinkTextLen="0" DOMCldNum="1" FontSize="12" FontWeight="400" BgColor="transparent" ObjectRectLeft="10" ObjectRectTop="632" ObjectRectWidth="413" ObjectRectHeight="95" Content="Thank you for agreeing to review a paper for ACM Transactions on Graphics. The editorial board of TOG is committed to publishing the most interesting and stimulating papers in computer graphics. We do this by reviewing papers with great care and expertise, and carrying out that reviewing and publishing efficiently and rapidly. " SRC="
&lt;P&gt;&lt;B&gt;Thank you&lt;/B&gt; for agreeing to review a paper for &lt;EM&gt;ACM Transactions on Graphics&lt;/EM&gt;. The editorial board of TOG is committed to publishing the most interesting and stimulating papers in computer graphics. We do this by reviewing papers with great care and expertise, and carrying out that reviewing and publishing efficiently and rapidly.&lt;/P&gt; " ID="1-2-1-1" order="32"/><LayoutNode FrameSourceIndex="0" SourceIndex="59" DoC="10" ContainImg="0" IsImg="false" ContainTable="false" ContainP="0" TextLen="276" LinkTextLen="0" DOMCldNum="1" FontSize="12" FontWeight="400" BgColor="transparent" ObjectRectLeft="10" ObjectRectTop="746" ObjectRectWidth="413" ObjectRectHeight="95" Content="Efficient reviewing is essential to the success of TOG. To publish papers in a timely fashion, we allow 30 days from receipt of the paper to prepare a TOG review. It is important that you commit to this timeframe. Otherwise the entire publication pipeline begins to slow down. " SRC="
&lt;P&gt;&lt;B&gt;Efficient reviewing&lt;/B&gt; is essential to the success of TOG. To publish papers in a timely fashion, we allow &lt;EM&gt;30 days&lt;/EM&gt; from receipt of the paper to prepare a TOG review. It is important that you commit to this timeframe. Otherwise the entire publication pipeline begins to slow down.&lt;/P&gt; " ID="1-2-1-2" order="33"/><LayoutNode FrameSourceIndex="0" SourceIndex="62" DoC="10" ContainImg="0" IsImg="false" ContainTable="false" ContainP="0" TextLen="343" LinkTextLen="0" DOMCldNum="1" FontSize="12" FontWeight="400" BgColor="transparent" ObjectRectLeft="10" ObjectRectTop="860" ObjectRectWidth="413" ObjectRectHeight="114" Content="Encourage diversity in our published papers and you will help make TOG interesting. We want to also encourage creative and imaginative papers, those that stimulate and provoke as well as enlighten. We will stand in the mainstream, but also welcome papers that are clever, or surprising, or present radical new directions for computer graphics. " SRC="
&lt;P&gt;&lt;B&gt;Encourage diversity&lt;/B&gt; in our published papers and you will help make TOG interesting. We want to also encourage creative and imaginative papers, those that stimulate and provoke as well as enlighten. We will stand in the mainstream, but also welcome papers that are clever, or surprising, or present radical new directions for computer graphics.&lt;/P&gt; " ID="1-2-1-3" order="34"/><LayoutNode FrameSourceIndex="0" SourceIndex="64" DoC="10" ContainImg="0" IsImg="false" ContainTable="false" ContainP="0" TextLen="417" LinkTextLen="0" DOMCldNum="1" FontSize="12" FontWeight="400" BgColor="transparent" ObjectRectLeft="10" ObjectRectTop="993" ObjectRectWidth="413" ObjectRectHeight="133" Content="Review compassionately and you can make the difference between a mediocre paper lost forever and one that is revised to publication quality and contributes to the field. Please write reviews that are meaningful for the author. Speak in particulars, not generalities. Never characterize the authors. Give constructive criticism when discussing a problem. If there are major flaws, identify them as clearly as possible. " SRC="
